tafsir[28]{c,v,t}:
  71,1,"Men imminii Nuuhu haa e yim…ďe makko …ďen, fii noddugol …ďe jertina …ďe, ado lette muusu…óe arde e ma…ď…ďe, sabu ko …ďe woni e sirkannde kon Allah."
  71,2,"Nuuhu maakani yim…ďe makko …ďen : ko onon yo yim…ďe am, min ko mi jertinoowo on, …ďanngin…óo jertinaango lette habbitii…ói on, si tawii on tuubanaali Allah."
  71,3,"Jertinaango am ngon, ko wi'ugol on : rewee Allah tun, hara on kafidaali Mo e go…ó…óum goo, huliron Mo …óoftagol yamiraa…ói Makko e wo…ó…óitagol ha…óaa…ói Makko, …óofto…óon lam e ko mi yamirta on kon."
  71,4,"Si on wa…óii …óum, Allah haforanany on junuubi mon …ói humondiraa…ói e haqqeeji jeyaa…ďe …ďen, O juutina laje mofte mon …óen haa e happu mo Allah anndi, nguurnon leydi fotde hi…óon √Īii…ďi e …óum. Ko woni tun, maayde nden si hewtii, ngal nennetaake, si …óon anndunoo …óum, on tii…ónorayno gom…óingol Allah, tuubun e sirku e majjere ko won…óon e mun."
  71,5,"Nuuhu maaki : Joomi am, mi jokkindirii noddirgol yim…ďe am …ďen e rewugol Ma e wootin…óine, jemma e √Īalorma ko ewindii."
  71,6,"Kono noddaandu am ndun …ďeydaani …ďe, si wanaa dogugol w…ó…óitoo ko mi noddata …ďe e mun kon."
  71,7,"Tuma kala kadi nde mi noddi …ďe e ko …ďe haforantee junuubi : wano rewugol Ma An tun, …óofto Maa An e Nulaa…óo Maa on, …ďe uddira noppi ma…ď…ďe …óin kollin …óin fii wata …ďe nanu, …ďe buumora comci ma…ď…ďe …óin fii wata …ďe yi'am, …ďe duumii e sirkugol ngol, …ďe townitanii ja…ďugol noddaandu am ndun, mawnintinanoo ndu."
  71,8,"Refti Joomi am, mi noddirii …ďee e kene."
  71,9,"Refti mi townanii …ďe hito ka noddugol, mi gunndii …ďe gunndagol, mi noddiri …ďe noone fow."
  71,10,"Mi wi*ani …ďe : ko onon yo yim…ďe am, …óa…ď…ďiree Joomi mon tuubaneede, tawde O siforii wonnde Haforoowo junuubi kala tuubu…óo e jeyaa…ďe Makko …ďen."
  71,11,"Si on wa…óii …óum, Allah jippiniray to…ďo ngon e moo…óon, jokkondiral tuma haaju mon yani e maggo, hara on he…ďataa kokke."
  71,12,"O ye…óay on jawle e …ďi…ó…ďe …óuu…óu…ďe, O wa…óana on gese …óe √Īaamoton dim…óe mun, O wa…óana on can…ói ka yaron yarnon gese e neemoraa…ói mon."
  71,13,"E ko he…ďi on yim…ďe am, on hulataa manngural Allah ngal, hi…óon yeddiral Mo yawitaare?"
  71,14,"Gom…óii le O tagirii on sagara-sagara, immorde e maniyyu, hooti he…ó…óere, hooti huyre."
  71,15,"E on yi'aali no Allah tagiri kammuuli jee…ói…ói tegondir…ói, kammu kala ina e hoore nguya?"
  71,16,"O wa…ói lewru ndun ka kammu aduna, ina heen ndaygu yim…ďe leydi ndin; O wa…ói naange ngen kadi ndayginnge."
  71,17,"Ko Allah tagiri e leydi ndin e tagugol baaba mon Aadama e mayri, hooti ko e mayri wuurdaton ko ndi funnata."
  71,18,"Refti O ruttiray on e mayri …ďaawo on maayude, O yaltinira ummintineede e mayre yaltudee."
  71,19,"Allah wa…óiranii on leydi ndin weertaandi hebliraandi ka ho…óee."
  71,20,"Fii no naatiron e mayri laawi yaaju…ói, ka …óa…ď…ďiron arsike dagii…óo."
  71,21,"Nuuhu maaki : Joomi am, yim…ďe am …ďen salanike lam e ko mi yamiri …ďe wootin…óingol Ma rewa Maa kon An tun. Jaasu…ďe …ďen e ma…ď…ďe jokki hooree…ďe …ďe neeminir…óaa …ďen e ma…ď…ďe jawle e …ďi…ó…ďe. Hara le kon ko neeminir…óaa …ďe …ďeydaali …ďe si wanaa majjere."
  71,22,"Hooree…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďen fewji feere mawnde, fii no …ďe cuynira jaasu…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďen e Nuuhu."
  71,23,"∆Āe wi'ani jokku…ďe …ďen : wata on terto dey rewetee…ói mon …óin : wata on terto rewugol sanamuuji mon …óin Wudda, e Suwaa'a, e Ya'uuqhta, e Nasr."
  71,24,"Ko pellet, …ďe majjinirii yim…ďe …óuu…óu…ďe, …óii sanamuuji ma…ď…ďe. Joomi, wata A …ďeydir too√Īir…ďe ko'e mun …ďen geddi e keeferaaku, si wanaa majjugol goonga."
  71,25,"Ko sabu goopi ma…ď…ďe …ói …ďe faggitinoo …óin, …ďe yoliranoo waame …óen, …ďe naadoyaa kisan ka Yiite …ďaawo maayde ma…ď…ďe. ∆Āe he…ďanaano ko'e ma…ď…ďe ko wanaa Allah, dan…óndoowo …ďe yoolagol e sumgol."
  71,26,"Nde Allah humpitunoo Nuuhu wonnde hay gooto gom…óintaa e yim…ďe maa …ďen si wanaa …ďeya gom…óinnoo…ďe, O maaki kadi: Joomi am, wata A accu e leydi ndin, hay keefeere gooto yiilatoo…óo wollo dilloowo."
  71,27,"Ko pellet, si A nennanii …ďe An Joomi amen, …ďe majjinoyay jeyaa…ďe Maa gom…óim…ďe …ďen, …ďe jiidoytaako kadi si wanaa bonnoo…ďe …ďe …óoftotaako Ma, tii…óu…ďe yeddugol …ďe yettatah neemaaji Maa …óin."
  71,28,"Joomi am, haforanam junuubi am, min e jibim…ďe lam …ďen, haforanaa kala gom…óin…óo naatu…óo ka suudu am, e gom…óim…ďe wor…ďe …ďen e gom…óim…ďe rew…ďe …ďen; wata A …ďeydir too√Īir…ďe ko'e mun …ďen geddi e leeferaaku, si wanaa halkagol e hayrugol."
